{
  "stem": "802.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was just before the war broke out, and they were rather poor people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, not-- not abjectly poor, but relatively poor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They also had a tiny apartment, and-- and-- But he was-- both he and his-- his-- his brother were very bright.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want to interject something, I hope it's all right, because I'm afraid I'm going to forget.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, I wanted to show you a photograph.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I'm going, perhaps, to ask my husband to help me with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "These two brothers were-- one of them was a communist, the older one was a communist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was working very arduously and he was arrested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was also an intellectual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were my mother's sister's son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All together, we're six children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two girls, we were the youngest ones, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my-- I'll give them names, David, or Dudek, as we used to call him, and Yosek, which is Joseph.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK, so Joseph, or Yosek, was the communist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was married just before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And during the war-- that is not during the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the Germans entered Poland, when they begin to bomb Warsaw, they fled to Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Russia was the only country at the time that allowed, opened the doors, to Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they prevailed upon my father to flee with them because my father was somewhat prominent, having been one of two people who were allowed to test the gold.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he was fairly well-known.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father ultimately agreed, even though he didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He fled with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was during the bombing in September 1939.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But after a week, he returned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, because he left the wife and two children, and so he just walked back.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
